      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just social media though. it's like they've already decided who i am, and it's like everyone's talking behind my back even when i'm not online. i walk down the halls and i can just feel it. like i'm just a joke to everyone. it's not something i can just \"log off\" from. it feels like the whole world is just one big room and i'm the only one being mocked. i just want the noise to stop. i want everything to just stop.",
