      "content": "i know you can't help me like that, but it's just frustrating because even talking about it feels like more noise. it doesn't change the fact that tomorrow is just gonna be more of the same. i'm just stuck in this loop where everything is bad and it's never gonna get better. what's the point of trying to \"reach out\" when the people you'd reach out to are probably the ones making you feel this way in the first place? it feels like there's no real escape from it.",
